ah, falau lâ nafara ming kulli firqatim min-hum thâ&#x27;ifatul liyatafaqqahû fid-dîni wa liyundzirû qaumahum idzâ raja‘û ilaihim la‘allahum yaḫdzarûn</span><span class="block text-md lg:text-lg text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300">Tidak sepatutnya orang-orang mukmin pergi semuanya (ke medan perang). Mengapa sebagian dari setiap golongan di antara mereka tidak pergi (tinggal bersama Rasulullah) untuk memperdalam pengetahuan agama mereka dan memberi peringatan kepada kaumnya apabila mereka telah kembali, agar mereka dapat menjaga dirinya?</span></div></div></div><div class="bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900/30 last:border-none border-b border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800 py-3 px-3 md:px-5 flex flex-col " id="123"><div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2"><span class=" text-primary-400 dark:text-primary-300 text-xl md:text-2xl">123<!-- -->.</span><div class="nui-ActionVerse "><div class="flex space-x-2.5 rtl:space-x-reverse items-center"><a href="/at-taubah/123" class="__className_80e47c text-sm px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full border border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-600 hover:bg-neutral-300 hover:dark:bg-neutral-600 hover">Tafsir</a><div class="nui-ButtonPlay select-none "><div class="inline-flex items-center py-0.5 cursor-pointer rounded-full transition-all"><span class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 hover:bg-neutral-200 dark:hover:bg-neutral-900 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon" class="w-5 h-5"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.5 5.653c0-1.427 1.529-2.33 2.779-1.643l11.54 6.347c1.295.712 1.295 2.573 0 3.286L7.28 19.99c-1.25.687-2.779-.217-2.779-1.643V5.653Z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></div></div><div><div class="inline-block text-left" data-headlessui-state><button class="text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full  h