ûn\",\"translation_en\":\"But when He gave them from His bounty, they were stingy with it and turned away while they refused.\",\"translation_de\":\"Als Er ihnen aber von Seiner Huld gewährt hatte, geizten sie damit, und sie kehrten sich widerstrebend ab.\",\"translation_tr\":\"Fakat Allah lütfundan onlara (zenginlik) verince, onda cimrilik edip (Allah'ın emrinden) yüz çevirerek sözlerinden döndüler.\",\"translation_fr\":\"Mais quand Il les eut comblés de Ses grâces, ils en furent avares et se rétractèrent en se détournant.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":4,\"end\":6},{\"class\":\"madd-jaiz\",\"start\":7,\"end\":10},{\"class\":\"idgham-mimi\",\"start\":17,\"end\":22},{\"class\":\"ikhfa\",\"start\":23,\"end\":28},{\"class\":\"idgham-mimi\",\"start\":68,\"end\":73},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":80,\"end\":82}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":75}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"76\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":1312,\"number\":77,\"text\":\"فَاَعْقَبَهُمْ نِفَاقًا فِيْ قُلُوْبِهِمْ اِلٰى يَوْمِ يَلْقَوْنَهٗ بِمَآ اَخْلَفُوا اللّٰهَ مَا وَعَدُوْهُ وَبِمَا كَانُوْا يَكْذِبُوْنَ\",\"translation_id\":\"Maka, (akibat kekikiran itu) Dia menanamkan kemunafikan dalam hati mereka sampai pada hari mereka menemui-Nya karena mereka telah mengingkari janji yang telah mereka ikrarkan kepada-Nya dan (juga) karena mereka selalu berdusta.\",\"juz_id\":10,\"surah_id\":9,\"transliteration\":\"fa a‘qabahum nifâqan fî qulûbihim ilâ yaumi yalqaunahû bimâ akhlafullâha mâ wa‘adûhu wa bimâ kânû yakdzibûn\",\"translation_en\":\"So He penalized them with hypocrisy in their hearts until the Day they will meet Him - because they failed Allāh in what they promised Him and because they [habitually] used to lie.\",\"translation_de\":\"So setzte Er als Folge davon in ihre Herzen Heuchelei bis zum Tag, an dem sie Ihm begegnen werden, dafür, daß sie gegenüber Allah brachen, was sie Ihm versprochen hatten, und daß sie zu lügen pflegten.\",\"translation_tr\":\"Nihayet, Allah'a verdikleri sözden döndü