lar vardır ki, münafıklıkta maharet kazanmışlardır. Sen onları bilmezsin, biz biliriz onları. Onlara iki kez azap edeceğiz, sonra da onlar büyük bir azaba itileceklerdir.\",\"translation_fr\":\"Parmi les bédouins qui sont autour de vous, et parmi les habitants de Médine, il est des hypocrites qui persistent obstinément dans l’hypocrisie. Tu ne saurais les reconnaître mais Nous les connaissons. Nous les soumettrons par deux fois au châtiment, puis ils seront voués à un terrible supplice.\",\"tajweed\":[{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":2,\"end\":4},{\"class\":\"idgham-mimi\",\"start\":18,\"end\":23},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":100,\"end\":102},{\"class\":\"idgham-mimi\",\"start\":163,\"end\":168},{\"class\":\"ghunnah\",\"start\":181,\"end\":183},{\"class\":\"madd-arid-lissukun\",\"start\":215,\"end\":217}]},\"surah\":\"$20\",\"index\":100}],[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"101\",{\"verse\":{\"id\":1337,\"number\":102,\"text\":\"وَاٰخَرُوْنَ اعْتَرَفُوْا بِذُنُوْبِهِمْ خَلَطُوْا عَمَلًا صَالِحًا وَّاٰخَرَ سَيِّئًاۗ عَسَى اللّٰهُ اَنْ يَّتُوْبَ عَلَيْهِمْۗ اِنَّ اللّٰهَ غَفُوْرٌ رَّحِيْمٌ\",\"translation_id\":\"(Ada pula) orang-orang lain yang mengakui dosa-dosanya. Mereka mencampuradukkan amal yang baik dengan amal lain yang buruk. Mudah-mudahan Allah menerima tobatnya. Sesungguhnya Allah Maha Pengampun lagi Maha Penyayang.\",\"juz_id\":11,\"surah_id\":9,\"transliteration\":\"wa âkharûna‘tarafû bidzunûbihim khalathû ‘amalan shâliḫaw wa âkhara sayyi'â, ‘asallâhu ay yatûba ‘alaihim, innallâha ghafûrur raḫîm\",\"translation_en\":\"And [there are] others who have acknowledged their sins. They had mixed [i.e., polluted] a righteous deed with another that was bad. Perhaps Allāh will turn to them in forgiveness. Indeed, Allāh is Forgiving and Merciful.\",\"translation_de\":\"Und (es gibt) andere, die ihre Sünden bekennen. Sie haben eine rechtschaffene Tat mit einer anderen bösen vermischt. Vielleicht wird Allah ihre Reue annehmen. Gewiß, Allah ist Allvergebend und Barmherzig.\",\"trans